Key changes made:

1. Changed `xmlns:xlink` to `xmlnsXlink`
2. Changed the style attribute from a string to an object with camelCase properties
3. Added the `className` prop to each SVG element
4. Added a default case that returns null
5. Removed unnecessary path IDs to clean up the code
6. Fixed indentation

This should now work without any errors. The component will render the appropriate icon based on the name prop passed to it, and can be styled using the optional className prop.
